        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> Well undying are my most popular hunting place....best to grp up with a druid and have a dire charmed snake...druid always snares and i NEVER gott a warp back till now...managed to kill the whole front of them. If you want to solo it, get a hp buff from somewhere and just use Thrall of bones. Pull with Thrall of bones and just move a bit back...use ur lvl 55 augement on ur pet and hope charm will hold long enough.<BR>I mostly get 3 mobs when i pull, so 1 is my pet and 2 adds. dont slow them, just let them beat up each other. Also there is a little order how u have to pull them for not getting more than 3 at 1 time. Hard to explain the order but if ya spend 1 day there u will figure it out which mobs ya have to pull next for not getting many adds.<BR>I just love undying iksars</P><P>Sage Seelendieb Soultaker<BR>Warlock<BR>Emarr</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
